    {
      "id": "sybil_1_listing_1",
      "firm_id": "sybil_1",
      "description": "Hey there! I am honestly so sad to let this beauty go, but it\u2019s time for a new home. This car is in absolutely incredible shape\u2014it\u2019s been babied since day one and honestly looks like it just rolled off the showroom floor! No scratches, no dents, and the interior is still totally pristine. It drives like an absolute dream and still has that fresh feel. If you\u2019re looking for a ride that feels brand new, you\u2019ve found it. Come take a look and see for yourself!",
      "price": 46500.0,
