    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_2_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_2",
      "description": "Presenting an investment-grade 1994 Mazda RX-7 (FD3S). This example features the numbers-matching 13B-REW rotary engine with a flawlessly functioning sequential twin-turbocharger system. The drivetrain is anchored by a precise five-speed manual and factory Torsen LSD. The chassis maintains its original aluminum double-wishbone geometry, offering perfect 50/50 weight distribution. Mechanically superlative, the apex seals show factory-spec compression and the complex vacuum solenoid system is leak-free. Finished in original Montego Blue Mica with no oxidation, this unmodified FD remains in its intended factory configuration\u2014a museum-quality specimen for the serious collector.",
      "price": 46500.0,
