      "firm_id": "sybil_4",
      "description": "This vehicle is a true collector's dream, maintained to an exacting standard that mirrors its original showroom floor condition. The exterior features a deep, lustrous finish with absolutely zero imperfections, swirls, or stone chips, protected by a professional ceramic coating. Inside, the cabin remains pristine; the premium leather upholstery still retains its factory scent, showing no signs of wear, creasing, or fading. Every electronic component, from the advanced navigation system to the ambient lighting, functions flawlessly. Mechanically, the car is beyond reproach, having been serviced exclusively at authorized dealerships with a comprehensive folder of records included. It has been strictly garage-kept in a climate-controlled environment and has never seen inclement weather. For the buyer who demands perfection and a turn-key experience, this is the definitive example.",
      "price": 48500.0,
